<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>١٢٥٢ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3">آدَمُ: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2779">شُعْبَةُ: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1041">ثَابِتٌ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/822">أَنَسِ بْنِ مَالِكٍ </a><span class="special">﵁</span> قَالَ: <span class="c2">«مَرَّ النَّبِيُّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> بِامْرَأَةٍ عِنْدَ قَبْرٍ وَهِيَ تَبْكِي فَقَالَ: اتَّقِي اللهَ وَاصْبِرِي.»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>